CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. B10, reads: "Chi Delta Mu Fraternity Entertains Lavishly - Dr. Leon Waddy, center rear; Mrs. Waddy, at his side, and guests." Portion of accompanying article by Toki Schalk Johnson reads: "Wednesday brought forth the annual dinner dance given by the Chi Delta Mu Fraternity in beautifully decorated New Arena..."
TitMainTitle: Group at Chi Delta Mu dinner dance, left side of table, from left: Huett M. Fleming, Pauline Crawford, Marsolete Wall Fleming, Mable Waddy, Dr. Leon Waddy; right side: Eloise Page, Clyde Page, Louisa Jeffries Webster Goode, James Goode, unknown; and Everett Utterback and Bernice Utterback in back, in New Arena Supper Club
